\[
8x_1 + 5x_2 + 3x_3 + 2x_4 \le 800
\]

---

### Logical Constraints

Robots and dolls cannot both be manufactured:
\[
y_1 + y_4 \le 1
\]

If model cars are manufactured, building blocks must also be manufactured:
\[
y_2 \le y_3
\]

Number of dolls cannot exceed number of model cars:
\[
x_4 \le x_2
\]

