  \[
  p_1=124,\; p_2=109,\; p_3=115
  \]
- Production cost (\$/100kg):  
  \[
  c_1=73.30,\; c_2=52.90,\; c_3=65.40
  \]
- Contribution margin per unit:  
  \[
  m_i = p_i - c_i
  \]
  \[
  m_1=50.7,\; m_2=56.1,\; m_3=49.6
  \]
- Daily production quota (units/day):  
  \[
  q_1=500,\; q_2=450,\; q_3=550
  \]
