  \[
  T=22
  \]
- Monthly capacity:  
  \[
  U_i = q_i \cdot T
  \]
  \[
  U_1=11000,\; U_2=9900,\; U_3=12100
  \]
- Fixed activation cost:  
  \[
  F_1=170000,\; F_2=150000,\; F_3=100000
  \]
- Minimum batch size:  
  \[
  L_1=20,\; L_2=20,\; L_3=16
  \]

