\[
1.25x_1 + 2.00x_2 + 2.80x_3
\]

#### Raw Material Cost
\[
0.25x_1 + 0.35x_2 + 0.50x_3
\]

#### Machine Operating Cost (proportional to used time)

Cost per hour:

\[
c_{A1}=\frac{300}{6000},\quad
c_{A2}=\frac{321}{10000},\quad
c_{B1}=\frac{250}{4000},\quad
c_{B2}=\frac{783}{7000},\quad
c_{B3}=\frac{200}{4000}
\]

Used time on each machine:

A1: \(5a_{1,1}+10a_{2,1}\)  
