【数学模型】:
 ### Decision Variables

Let  

For Product I:  
- \(x_{1A1}\) = quantity of product I processed on A1  
- \(x_{1A2}\) = quantity of product I processed on A2  
- \(x_{1B1}\) = quantity of product I processed on B1  
- \(x_{1B2}\) = quantity of product I processed on B2  
- \(x_{1B3}\) = quantity of product I processed on B3  

For Product II:  
- \(x_{2A1}\) = quantity of product II processed on A1  
- \(x_{2A2}\) = quantity of product II processed on A2  
- \(x_{2B1}\) = quantity of product II processed on B1  

For Product III:  
- \(x_{3A2}\) = quantity of product III processed on A2  
- \(x_{3B2}\) = quantity of product III processed on B2  

All variables ≥ 0.

---

### Flow Balance Constraints (Stage A = Stage B)

Product I:
\[
x_{1A1} + x_{1A2} = x_{1B1} + x_{1B2} + x_{1B3}
\]

Product II:
\[
x_{2A1} + x_{2A2} = x_{2B1}
\]

Product III:
\[
x_{3A2} = x_{3B2}
\]

---

### Machine Capacity Constraints

A1:
\[
5x_{1A1} + 10x_{2A1} \le 6000
\]

A2:
\[
7x_{1A2} + 9x_{2A2} + 12x_{3A2} \le 10000
\]

B1:
\[
6x_{1B1} + 8x_{2B1} \le 4000
\]

B2:
\[
4x_{1B2} + 11x_{3B2} \le 7000
\]

B3:
\[
7x_{1B3} \le 4000
\]

---

### Objective Function (Maximize Total Profit)

Revenue:
\[
1.25(x_{1A1}+x_{1A2})
+ 2(x_{2A1}+x_{2A2})
+ 2.8(x_{3A2})
\]

Raw material cost:
\[
0.25(x_{1A1}+x_{1A2})
+ 0.35(x_{2A1}+x_{2A2})
+ 0.5(x_{3A2})
\]

Processing cost:

Stage A cost:
\[
0.05(5x_{1A1}+10x_{2A1})
+ 0.03(7x_{1A2}+9x_{2A2}+12x_{3A2})
\]

Stage B cost:
\[
0.06(6x_{1B1}+8x_{2B1})
+ 0.11(4x_{1B2}+11x_{3B2})
+ 0.05(7x_{1B3})
\]

---

### Final LP Model

\[
\max Z =
\text{Revenue}
- \text{Raw Material Cost}
- \text{Processing Cost}
\]

i.e.,

\[
\max Z =
\]

\[
1.25(x_{1A1}+x_{1A2})
+ 2(x_{2A1}+x_{2A2})
+ 2.8x_{3A2}
\]

\[
-0.25(x_{1A1}+x_{1A2})
-0.35(x_{2A1}+x_{2A2})
-0.5x_{3A2}
\]

\[
-0.05(5x_{1A1}+10x_{2A1})
-0.03(7x_{1A2}+9x_{2A2}+12x_{3A2})
\]

\[
-0.06(6x_{1B1}+8x_{2B1})
-0.11(4x_{1B2}+11x_{3B2})
-0.05(7x_{1B3})
\]

