3 Yuan vase | 20000  
4 Porsche 911 | 40000  
5 Diamond 1 | 12000  
6 Diamond 2 | 12000  
7 Diamond 3 | 12000  
8 Louis XV sofa | 3000  
9 Dog 1 | 3000  
10 Dog 2 | 3000  
