Substitute \(S_2 = V - S_1\):

\[
S_1 - (V - S_1) \le t
\]

\[
(V - S_1) - S_1 \le t
\]

Which simplifies to:

\[
2S_1 - V \le t
\]

\[
V - 2S_1 \le t
\]

---

### Dog inseparability constraint

Dogs must go together:

\[
x_9 = x_{10}
\]

---

### Binary constraints

\[
x_i \in \{0,1\}, \quad \forall i \in I
\]

\[
t \ge 0
\]

