Model B (at least 15):

\[
x_2 + d_3^- - d_3^+ = 15
\]

---

### (3) Process utilization goals

Process I (exactly 150 hours):

\[
4x_1 + 6x_2 + d_4^- - d_4^+ = 150
\]

Process II (fully utilized, overtime allowed):

\[
3x_1 + 2x_2 + d_5^- - d_5^+ = 70
\]

