## Preemptive Objective Function

Given priority structure  
\[
p_1 \succ p_2 \succ p_3
\]

\[
\min Z =
P_1 d_1^-
+ P_2 (d_2^- + d_3^-)
+ P_3 (d_4^- + d_4^+ + d_5^-)
\]

where  

