P_1 \gg P_2 \gg P_3
\]

Interpretation:

- Priority 1: Minimize profit shortfall.
- Priority 2: Minimize violations of contractual minimum production.
- Priority 3: 
  - Enforce exact use of Process I (penalize both over/under use).
  - Minimize idle time in Process II (penalize \(d_5^-\) only).

---

## Nonnegativity

\[
