Processing times \( t_{ij} \):

\[
\begin{array}{c|ccc}
 & M1 & M2 & M3 \\
\hline
1 & 2 & 3 & 1 \\
2 & 4 & 2 & 3 \\
3 & 3 & 5 & 2 \\
\end{array}
\]

Let \(M\) be a sufficiently large constant.

