- \(L_s\) = labor days used for external work in spring & summer  
- \(L_a\) = labor days used for external work in autumn & winter  

(All decision variables \(\ge 0\); \(x_4, x_5\) can be restricted to integers if required.)

---

### Objective Function

Maximize total annual net income:

